 & =(cu_{1},cu_{2},\ldots,cu_{n})\ \bcdot\ v_{1},v_{2},\ldots,v_{n}\\
 & =cu_{1}v_{1}+cu_{2}v_{2}+\cdots+cu_{n}v_{n}\\
 & =c(u_{1}v_{1}+u_{2}v_{2}+\cdots+u_{n}v_{n})\\
